pwkickstart

Helps to generate kickstart passwords.

SYNOPSIS

  # pwkickstart 
  Password: 

  # md5
  rootpw --iscrypted $1$SI7hD964QyK1.Iz/
  # sha256
  rootpw --iscrypted $5$eqAC4DfizzLlEwUQI3/Q6SEYqHGso3maNbtBc1wjyiyr2
  # sha512
  rootpw --iscrypted $6$MN7wS1QE3FYNZbOS19HfAN0JiloK6s24mSBrN71tXV8y.Blif1avdhTYt/

The output was shortened to fit 80 columns in the example above.

WHY

Because grub-crypt is no longer available in Fedora and RHEL 7+.

AUTHOR

Lukas Zapletal <lzap+spam@redhat.com>

